 # CSS Conventions
 
-This project uses custom CSS conventions. Layouts use a `data-rack` attribute system.
+## Common Failures
+
+- FAILURE: Using standard CSS grid/flex without `data-rack` attributes. Layouts MUST use the `data-rack` container system.
+- FAILURE: Writing raw CSS animations without `data-zap` attributes. All motion uses the custom animation attribute system.
+- FAILURE: Using hardcoded colors instead of `--ink-` custom properties. Theming breaks without the `data-coat` system.
 
