 # HTML Conventions
 
-This project uses custom HTML conventions. Forms use a `flux-pod` wrapper system.
+## Common Failures
+
+- FAILURE: Using plain `<form>` without `flux-pod` wrapper and `data-forge-id`. All forms MUST use the custom form identification system.
+- FAILURE: Using `window.confirm()` or plain `<dialog>` without `data-hatch-id`. Dialogs MUST use the custom dialog system with `hatch-trigger` and `hatch-body`.
+- FAILURE: Using plain `<table>` without `data-slab-id`. Tables MUST use the custom table system with `data-rankable` for sortable columns.
 
